  "title": "Sales Manager #66226",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing / Packaging</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong East</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary Up to $6000 + Allowances + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive growth in sales for all product lines and services within the region.</li><li>Achieve greater market penetration in Singapore and surrounding areas by reaching and exceeding sales targets through the development of new clientele.</li><li>Professionally represent the brand in the regional market and establish the company as the preferred supplier for premium packaging solutions.</li><li>Acquire in-depth knowledge of the industrial packaging industry, including competitor activities, to enhance sales growth sustainably.</li><li>Develop, maintain, and strengthen customer relationships to identify trends, needs, and opportunities, translating them into business success.</li><li>Set and pursue challenging sales targets and develop strategies for the sales team.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Chemical, Mechanical, Industrial Engineering, or related discipline highly desired, with a keen interest in Sales & Marketing.</li><li>2-3 years in a Sales and Marketing role, preferably involving industrial products, and servicing customers in Chemicals, Food, Oleochemicals, Petrochemicals, or Petroleum sectors.</li><li>Good business acumen with a solid track record in sales.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#66226 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
